Janelle Timmins

Home

Untitled

There was a woman called Janelle

Who thought she was rather swell

She has just written a novel

Which is really awful

And it probably wont even sell

Affirmicon

Janelle's Story

I arrived on Ramsay Street

And Stayed with best friend Lyn

I wouldn't admit defeat

By cheating tyrant Kim

I didn't want to leave

But Lyn had had enough

With Kim not on the scene

Things were gonna be a bit rough

As soon as Joe Mangel departed

We could all finally relax

I might not be good-hearted

So he better watch his tracks

Edward Skylover
